'''[[Doctor of Medicine|Dr.]] Sulaiman bin Abdulaziz Al-Habib''' ({{lang-ar|الدكتور سليمان بن عبد العزيز الحبيب}}; born on the [[20th century]] in [[Jeddah]], [[Saudi Arabia]]) is the founder and the Chairman of Dr. Sulaiman Al-Habib Medical Group which owns and operates a number of hospitals and medical centers in [[Saudi Arabia|Kingdom of Saudi Arabia]], [[United Arab Emirates]] and [[Kingdom of Bahrain]]. Dr. Sulaiman Al-Habib, M.R.C.P.
(UK), D.C.H. (London), is a Pediatric Consultant.
He has practiced  in the [[United Kingdom]] and the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia. He is also a co-owner and board member of Mohammad Al Habib Real Estate Co., a company which owns a number of real estate projects in KSA.

'''Work experience and key positions:'''
* Chief of Medical Staff at [[King Saud University#King Khalid University Hospital|King Khalid University Hospital]], [[Riyadh]].
* Chairman of the Pediatric Department at Security Forces Hospital, Riyadh.
* Consultant Pediatrician & Pediatric Endocrinologist at King Saud University, Riyadh
* In the year 1995, Dr. Al Habib established Dr Sulaiman Al Habib Medical Group.
* Senior Medical Consultant in the Ministry of Health, Riyadh.
* President of the Medical Committee and board member in Riyadh Chamber of Commerce and Industry.

